 166:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c **** /*
 167:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  * Unlocks a queue locked by a call to prvLockQueue.  Locking a queue does not
 168:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  * prevent an ISR from adding or removing items to the queue, but does prevent
 169:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  * an ISR from removing tasks from the queue event lists.  If an ISR finds a
 170:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  * queue is locked it will instead increment the appropriate queue lock count
 171:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  * to indicate that a task may require unblocking.  When the queue in unlocked
 172:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  * these lock counts are inspected, and the appropriate action taken.
 173:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  */
