 234:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c **** /*
 235:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  * If a task waiting for a mutex causes the mutex holder to inherit a
 236:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  * priority, but the waiting task times out, then the holder should
 237:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  * disinherit the priority - but only down to the highest priority of any
 238:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  * other tasks that are waiting for the same mutex.  This function returns
 239:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  * that priority.
 240:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****  */
