2820:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****          * It can result in vListInsert() being called on a list that can only
2821:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****          * possibly ever have one item in it, so the list will be fast, but even
2822:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****          * so it should be called with the scheduler locked and not from a critical
2823:middlewares/freertos/source/queue.c ****          * section. */
